sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Card as ShareCardGenerator
    participant DOM as DOM节点
    participant H2C as html2canvas
    participant Clipboard as navigator.clipboard

    Note over User,Clipboard: 用户在记录详情中点击"分享"
    Card->>DOM: 创建临时分享卡片DOM（物品名+¥/天+DayCost水印）
    Card->>DOM: 设置尺寸为社交分享尺寸（1080x1080或640x640）
    Card->>H2C: html2canvas(tempElement, {scale: 2, useCORS: true})
    H2C-->>Card: Canvas对象
    Card->>Card: addWatermark(canvas) — 底部水印条"DayCost · 日摊成本看板"
    Card->>Card: canvas.toBlob('image/png')

    alt 用户选择下载
        Card->>User: 创建<a download="daycost-share.png">触发下载
    else 用户选择复制
        Card->>Clipboard: clipboard.write([new ClipboardItem({blob})])
        Card->>User: Toast提示"已复制到剪贴板"
    end

    Card->>DOM: 移除临时DOM节点
